				<div class="book-name">The Second Epistle of the Blessed Apostle Paul to the Corinthians </div>
				<div class="act-chapter">
					<div class="prev-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200221103111/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/2_Cor/8072">&lt; prev</a></div>|
					<div class="chapter">Chapter 12</div>
					|<div class="next-chapter"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20200221103111/http://catholicbible.online/knox/NT/2_Cor/8074">next &gt;</a></div>
